title: Pokemon Insurgence 1.0.12.zip
description:
The latest Pokemon Insurgence binary. (1.0.12)

It's a freely available fan game in beta stage, but took me quite long to download, presumably due to slow or otherwise problematic servers. Maybe overloaded? Who knows.

Resharing here just so you don't have to wait for aeons, if your download is slow as well.

More info at: http://pokemoninsurgence.wikia.com/wiki/Pokemon_Insurgence_Wiki
